<a href="http://home.earthlink.net/~jpsohl/gclogo.gif"><img SRC="gclogos.gif" HSPACE=4 height=261 width=220 align=ABSCENTER></a><font size=+3>Goose
Club of the Alpha Inn</font>
<p>The Goose Club of the Alpha Inn, founded in 1977, is one of several
Sherlock Holmes societies based in the Los Angeles area.
<p><b>This page last updated 24 August 2006.</b>
<br>
<hr width="100%">
<p><a href="http://www.latimes.com/HOME/BUSINESS/PICK/" target="TimesWindow"><img SRC="timepick.gif" ALT="LOS ANGELES TIMES PICK" BORDER=0 height=96 width=96 align=LEFT></a>This
site was awarded a Times Pick by the <b>Los Angeles Times</b> on 1/6/97.
Standards for Web excellence were lower in those days.
<p>
